Date and Time Grouping, Tool Panels Displayed Outside of grid, Expand/Collapse all group rows in the server-side row model, Clipboard and Row Dragging Improvements.

## What's New

AG Grid {% migrationVersion() %} adds important new features – [Date and Time Grouping](./grouping-data/#grouping-by-dates-and-times), [Tool Panels Displayed Outside of grid](./side-bar/#tool-panel-parent), [Expand/Collapse all group rows in the server-side row model](./server-side-model-grouping/#expand-all--collapse-all), Clipboard and Row Dragging Improvements as described in the [release post](https://blog.ag-grid.com/whats-new-in-ag-grid-34-2/).

These improvements involve no breaking changes as listed below.

